{"tid":1320747,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[任地獄] 分析師：冷靜過後NSLite多被視作PSV後繼機 前途未必明朗","createTime":"2019-07-15T12:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T02:09:14.000Z","uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f04c755064bff10260d3a21875b231644ed45b17","tid":1320747,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2380061715597669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2380061715597669&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjay4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=2f2a1022\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2380061715597669</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqn7yd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxqn7yd3.png&h=56d47f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong><ins>【業界】分析師：冷靜過後NSLite多被視作PSV後繼機 前途未必明朗</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  前幾日，任天堂突然公佈了Switch的攜帶強化版Switch Lite。引發業界震動，玩家歡呼，任天堂股票大漲。然而當民眾逐漸冷靜下來後，普遍有種呼聲，Switch Lite實際上並不是被視作3DS的，而是已經折戟的PSV後繼機，且前途未必明朗。<br />\n<br />\n  7月15日今天，著名業界分析師河村鳴紘發表題為&ldquo;任天堂Switch Lite 被視為PSV後繼機的聲音潛藏的嚴酷現實&rdquo;的文章，客觀分析了Switch Lite的未來前景，一起來了解下。 （以下均為河村鳴紘的觀點）<br />\n<br />\n  <strong><ins>伴隨著Switch Lite的公佈，Vita也成了熱搜詞</ins></strong>，這裡的Vita當然是指索尼曾經的主機掌機PSV，雖然大家都覺得Switch Lite是任天堂自社3DS的次世代後繼掌機，不過實際上玩家們將其視作PSV後繼機的呼聲更強烈。<br />\n<br />\n  然而問題不是沒有，如今時代掌機賣的並不好，根據市調數字來看，<strong><ins>任天堂DS賣了1.5億台，而後繼機3DS縮減為7500萬台，索尼這邊，PSP賣了7600萬台，而後繼機PSV全球賣了多少台索尼並沒有明示，據FAMI通推算PSV在日本僅有590萬台的銷量</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n  不可否認的是，PSV的確是台好掌機，然而就是賣不動，擺在Switch Lite面前最大的課題就是能否賣的動？<strong><ins>不過任天堂的確很有策略，Switch Lite並非像PSV那樣脫離體係自成一派，本身有著Switch積累下的好口碑和海量遊戲的支援和更便宜的價格</ins></strong>，儘管悲觀系的聲音在不斷出現，筆者認為或許Switch Lite真正的敵人還是自社的3DS。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rncZ8No.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrncZ8No.png&h=76558ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>【NSLite】買前必看：4款無法使用Switch Lite遊玩的熱門遊戲</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1312781/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1312781/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[老任新機已出] Switch游戲太少? 任天堂最新發布的Switch宣傳片高調進行反駁!</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1303785/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1303785/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3009a5adb66ee3e116e0a15e0ccaf5ca73df4709","tid":1320747,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca99c39b33a96547b9911751796db58b4912ed7e","tid":1320747,"uid":36509,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"想問好耐<br />\n你日日轉貼個page啲post 無人理嗰陣又推返啲Post上來<br />\n其實個page係咪你開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係嘅話唔該你貼野前做好fact check<br />\n-「著名業界分析師河村鳴紘」 陰功囉google得幾頁result, 佢個blog 6月先開, 2ch有人轉貼你依篇嘅原文但都有人留言同佢邊撚個<br />\n- 有幾個result都係同你貼篇文用字完全一樣但早過你個page出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a38a78e990ac940c45d66f3148a0be495d2de92","tid":1320747,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"寫遊戲新聞雖然可以唔駛用腦<br />\n<br />\n但可唔可認真用一次腦咁多多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e4b2a1f06b9fa586dfd361a867de58bd719462","tid":1320747,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"係時候大手入v仔 今舖重唔fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01e69e8c73e58702e314783989577ce5568ef0d","tid":1320747,"uid":75050,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"ca99c39b33a96547b9911751796db58b4912ed7e","tid":1320747,"uid":36509,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:21:03